<div class="my-32">
  <div class="px-5">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold bg-gray-50">新手上路</h2>
    <h3 class="text-xl my-4">你好！歡迎來到RubyTix！</h3>
    <div class="text-lg my-2 w-2/6">
      <div>
        這裡會告訴你如何參加活動、購買票券，請依照下方指示操作。
        如有任何問題，請參閱<%= link_to '[常見問題]', faq_pages_path %>，若你的問題無法在本頁面獲得解答，歡迎與我們聯繫。
      </div>
      <div>
        聯絡信箱：<a href="mailto:contact@rubytix.fun">contact@rubytix.fun</a>
      </div>
      <div>客服(LINE@)服務時間：週一至週五(10:00~17:00)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="attend_act">
      <h3 class="text-2xl my-4">1.參加活動</h3>
      <ul class="list-decimal list-inside text-xl">
        <li class="my-8">在網站中查看感興趣的活動，點擊前往查看相關內容</li>
        <img src="/images/guide_find.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
        <li class="my-8">瀏覽活動頁面，確認活動內容</li> 
        <img src="/images/guide_check.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
        <li class="my-8">點擊「參加活動」按鈕</li> 
        <img src="/images/guide_attend.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
    </div>

    <div class="but_ticket">
      <h3 class="text-2xl my-4">2.購買票券</h3>
      <ul class="list-decimal list-inside text-xl">
        <li class="my-8">選擇欲購買票券，放入購物車</li>
        <img src="/images/guide_buy.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
        <li class="my-8">準備結帳</li>
        <img src="/images/guide_cart.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
        <li class="my-8">確認票券使用者資料</li>
        <img src="/images/guide_user.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
        <li class="my-8">進行結帳（LINEpay）</li>
        <img src="/images/guide_checkout.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="but_ticket">
      <h3 class="text-2xl my-4">3.查看訂單</h3>
      <ul class="list-decimal list-inside text-xl">
        <li class="my-8">查看訂單：點擊訂單可見票券內容</li>
        <img src="/images/guide_order.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
        <li class="my-8">查看票券內容</li>
        <img src="/images/guide_ticket.webp" width=500px height=500px alt="尋找活動" class="mx-6 border-black">
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-xl my-10 ml-20 text-3xl">恭喜你！準備參加活動吧!</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
